                   <p className="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Følg stegene under for å vise aktiviteten direkte i Canvas uten "vindu-i-vindu" problemer.</p>
               </div>
               <button onClick={onClose} className="text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600"><X size={24}/></button>
           </div>

           <div className="space-y-6 text-sm text-slate-600">
               {/* STEP 1 */}
               <div className="flex gap-3">
                   <div className="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-700 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
                   <div>
                       <p className="font-bold text-slate-800">Last ned filen</p>
                       <p className="mb-2">Last ned aktiviteten som en HTML-fil til din datamaskin.</p>
                       <button onClick={() => onDownload(activity)} className="px-3 py-1.5 bg-cyan-50 text-cyan-700 font-bold rounded-lg text-xs hover:bg-cyan-100 flex items-center gap-1 border border-cyan-200">
                           <Download size={14}/> Last ned .html
                       </button>
                   </div>
               </div>

               {/* STEP 2 */}
               <div className="flex gap-3">
                   <div className="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-700 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
                   <div>
                       <p className="font-bold text-slate-800">Last opp til Canvas</p>
                       <p>Gå til <strong>Filer</strong> i ditt Canvas-emne og last opp HTML-filen.</p>
                   </div>
               </div>

               {/* STEP 3 - LINK INPUT */}
               <div className="flex gap-3">
                   <div className="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-700 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
                   <div className="w-full">
                       <p className="font-bold text-slate-800">Kopier lenke fra "Filer"</p>
                       <p className="mb-2">Høyreklikk på filen i Canvas-filoversikten og velg <em>"Kopier lenkeadresse"</em>.</p>
                       <input 
                         type="text" 
                         value={userUrl} 
                         onChange={handleUrlChange}
                         placeholder="https://hvl.instructure.com/courses/.../files/..."
                         className={`w-full p-2 border rounded-lg text-xs font-mono outline-none transition-all ${warning ? 'border-amber-300 bg-amber-50 focus:border-amber-500' : 'border-slate-300 focus:border-cyan-500'}`}
                       />

                       {warning && (
                           <div className="mt-2 text-xs text-amber-700 bg-amber-50 p-2 rounded flex items-start gap-2 border border-amber-200">
                               <AlertTriangle size={14} className="mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"/>
                               <span>{warning}</span>
                           </div>
                       )}

                       {isFixed && !warning && (
                           <div className="mt-2 text-xs text-green-600 bg-green-50 p-2 rounded flex flex-col gap-1 border border-green-100">
                               <div className="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold">
                                   <Wand2 size={14}/> Lenke fikset og rekonstruert!
                               </div>
                               <div className="opacity-80 break-all text-[10px] font-mono pl-5">
                                   Vi fant Fil-IDen din og lagde en ren lenke som fjerner Canvas-menyene.
                               </div>
                           </div>
                       )}
                       {!userUrl && (
                           <div className="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-400 italic">Lim inn lenken for å generere koden.</div>
                       )}
                   </div>
               </div>

               {/* STEP 4 - CODE OUTPUT */}
               <div className="flex gap-3">
                   <div className="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-700 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">4</div>
                   <div className="w-full">
                       <p className="font-bold text-slate-800">Kopier kode</p>
                       <p className="mb-2">Opprett en ny Side, bytt til HTML-visning (<code>&lt;/&gt;</code>), og lim inn koden:</p>

                       <div className="bg-slate-800 text-slate-300 p-3 rounded-lg font-mono text-xs break-all relative group shadow-inner min-h-[60px] flex items-center">
                           {iframeCode}
                           <button onClick={() => navigator.clipboard.writeText(iframeCode)} className="absolute top-2 right-2 p-1.5 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded text-white transition-opacity opacity-70 hover:opacity-100" title="Kopier kode">
                               <Copy size={14}/>
                           </button>
                       </div>
                   </div>
               </div>
           </div>

           <div className="pt-4 border-t border-slate-100 flex justify-end">
               <button onClick={onClose} className="px-5 py-2.5 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 font-bold rounded-xl transition-colors">Lukk vindu</button>
